1. Who is the main character in the *first* quartet by Tamora Pierce?

[m_wrong] Your Answer: Giles of Aigidion


          The correct answer was Alanna of Trebond

          Keladry of Mindelan was the heroine in the quartet "Protector of the Small". The other two choices are made up.
          Alanna grew up in Fief Trebond with her twin brother Thom. Thom becomes a sorcerer and gets killed during Alanna's
          years as a knight.

