3. What color robe is Numair?

[m_check] Your Answer: Black


          Black robe is the highest that any sorcerer can achieve. At the time of "The Immortals" quartet, there were only
          seven in the world. It is a highly risky position, too. Numair is very old for a black robe, and he is only in his
          30s!

