4. What is the last book in "The Circle Opens" quartet called?

[m_wrong] Your Answer: Weather Mage


          The correct answer was Shatterglass

          I found this out by going to Amazon.com. I have too much time on my hands! This book is also in stores now, but only
          in hardback.

