8. What is Keladry's biggest fear?

[m_check] Your Answer: Heights


          Keladry is deathly afraid of heights until the end of "Page." She has to rescue her maid at the top of a tower, and
          afterwards only detests heights. It was better than before, when she would throw up or freeze near a cliff.

