9. Where does Alanna live?

[m_wrong] Your Answer: Yamani Islands


          The correct answer was Pirate's Swoop

          She moves into the Barony of Pirate's Swoop with her husband, George. George was given the property and title of
          Baron so that Jonathan wouldn't have to arrest him. George is good friends with Jonathan, although they fought over
          Alanna.

