10. Does Rosethorn die for good in the "Circle of Magic" quartet?

[m_wrong] Your Answer: y


          The correct answer was n

          She dies from the blue pox and is pulled back into life by Briar, Sandry, Tris, and Daja. Briar finds her tending a
          rambunctious garden in Death, and she seems not to want to leave. However, Briar loves her as a mother, and she can't
          go away!

